news.title: Pune: Maha Metro told to 'cover' Swargate concrete mix plant, prevent pollution
news.para: Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC) administrator Vikram Kumar said, “Precautionary measures need to be taken within three days of receiving the notice. The PMC may consider giving a stop-work order, if the Metro fails to take action within the stipulated time.”

news.title: Cement companies poised for stronger show in H2 FY24
news.para: The improved profitability in the September quarter, along with the expected improvement in the December and March quarters is expected to lift the average operating profit per tonne of cement makers to ₹970 per tonne in FY24 compared with ₹745 per tonne a year ago, Axis Securities said in a note.

news.title: Complete houses by February 2024, Andhra Pradesh CM tells officials
news.para: At a review meeting on housing on Thursday, the chief minister said the official machinery should act in such a way that identified problems are solved immediately.
